========================================
    INTRO
========================================

This is daemon.py, a Python implementation of the standard UNIX double-fork
technique. You will find abundant documentation inline in the module docstrings
and comments, online at http://www.zetadev.com/software/daemon.py/, and in the
doc/ directory of this distribution.


